DiskStats++ is an open source project dedicated to making available
to the wider galactic dynamics community (particularly theorists) a
set of analysis codes to efficiently analyze large data sets.   More
to come later.

Dependencies:  

GSL (after and including 1.16)
FFTW 3
gnuplot (if plots are wanted)

This project for some good palettes:
https://github.com/Gnuplotting/gnuplot-palettes

Credit to Anna Schneider for porting these.